## Key Learning

A clean and isolated environment is critical before starting ML/LLM development.

The Windows App Execution Alias issue can silently override the intended Python interpreter, so verifying which Python executable is being used is an important troubleshooting step whenever virtual environments appear to behave unexpectedly.
